, 744.0, 1103.7, 764.9]}, {"text": "and distributed during the years ended December 31, 2009, 2008 and 2007 was $0.6 million, $0.3 million and", "bbox": [153.2, 769.0, 1103.8, 789.9]}, {"text": "$0.5 million, respectively. The grant-date fair value is calculated based upon the Company’s closing stock price", "bbox": [153.2, 794.1, 1103.7, 814.9]}, {"text": "on the date of grant. As of December 31, 2009, 108,530 DSUs were unvested, with an aggregate intrinsic value", "bbox": [153.2, 819.1, 1103.7, 839.9]}, {"text": "of approximately $7.3 million and a weighted average remaining contractual life of approximately 1.3 years.", "bbox": [153.2, 844.1, 1103.7, 864.9]}, {"text": "These units are expected to vest through May 2011. All DSUs vest upon fulfilling service conditions or upon a", "bbox": [153.2, 869.1, 1103.8, 889.9]}, {"text": "director’s departure from the Board.", "bbox": [153.2, 894.1, 455.5, 914.9]}, {"text": "Restricted Stock Units", "bbox": [153.2, 936.8, 343.4, 957.7]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the different types of restricted stock units (“RSUs”) granted by the", "bbox": [194.9, 968.0, 1103.7, 988.8]}, {"text": "Company (in thousands):", "bbox": [153.2, 993.0, 364.1, 1013.8]}, {"text": "For the Years Ended December 31,", "bbox": [851.5, 1024.6, 1101.7, 1041.2]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [868.2, 1049.6, 901.6, 1066.2]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [959.9, 1049.6, 993.3, 1066.2]}, {"text": "2007", "bbox": [1051.7, 1049.6, 1085.0, 1066.2]}, {"text": "RSUs with service-based vesting conditions . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [153.2, 1079.9, 828.6, 1100.8]}, {"text": "2,342", "bbox": [861.5, 1079.9, 908.4, 1100.8]}, {"text": "1,529", "bbox": [953.2, 1079.9, 1000.1, 1100.8]}, {"text": "588", "bbox": [1060.5, 1079.9, 1091.8, 1100.8]}, {"text": "RSUs with performance-based vesting conditions . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [153.2, 1104.9, 828.6, 1125.8]}, {"text": "1,974", "bbox": [861.5, 1104.9, 908.4, 1125.8]}, {"text": "898", "bbox": [968.8, 1104.9, 1000.1, 1125.8]}, {"text": "1,409", "bbox": [1044.9, 1104.9, 1091.8, 1125.8]}, {"text": "Total . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [153.2, 1138.3, 828.6, 1159.1]}, {"text": "4,316", "bbox": [861.5, 1138.3, 908.4, 1159.1]}, {"text": "2,427", "bbox": [953.2, 1138.3, 1000.1, 1159.1]}, {"text": "1,997", "bbox": [1044.9, 1138.3, 1091.8, 1159.1]}, {"text": "RSUs represent the right to receive one share of the Company’s common stock upon vesting. RSUs are", "bbox": [194.9, 1187.7, 1103.7, 1208.5]}, {"text": "granted at the discretion of the Board of Directors, a committee thereof or, subject to defined limitations, the", "bbox": [153.2, 1212.7, 1103.7, 1233.5]}, {"text": "Chief Executive Officer of the Company to whom such authority has been delegated. The Company has issued", "bbox": [153.2, 1237.7, 1103.7, 1258.5]}, {"text": "RSUs that vest based on the passage of time assuming continued service with the Company, as well as RSUs that", "bbox": [153.2, 1262.7, 1103.7, 1283.5]}, {"text": "vest only upon the achievement of defined performance metrics tied to corporate revenue and earnings per share", "bbox": [153.2, 1287.7, 1103.7, 1308.6]}, {"text": "targets.", "bbox": [153.2, 1312.7, 214.0, 1333.6]}, {"text": "For RSUs with service-based vesting conditions, the fair value was calculated based upon the Company’s", "bbox": [194.9, 1349.6, 1103.7, 1370.5]}, {"text": "closing stock price on the date of grant, and the stock-based compensation expense is being recognized over the", "bbox": [153.2, 1374.6, 1103.7, 1395.5]}, {"text": "vesting period. Most RSUs with service-based vesting provisions vest in installments over a three- or four-year", "bbox": [153.2, 1399.6, 1103.6, 1420.5]}, {"text": "period following the grant date.", "bbox": [153.2, 1424.7, 417.0, 1445.5]}, {"text": "89", "bbox": [618.1, 1475.4, 638.9, 149